<h2>How to Request Account Deletion</h2>

<ol>
    <li>Send an email to our support team.</li>
    <li>Use the subject line <strong>"Delete My Account"</strong>.</li>
    <li>Include the email address associated with your Voiceee account.</li>
</ol>

<p class="email">
📧 support@voiceee.app
</p>

<h2>What Will Be Deleted</h2>

After verifying your request, we will permanently delete:

<ul>
    <li>Your account information</li>
    <li>Your profile information</li>
    <li>Your authentication data</li>
    <li>Any user data associated with your account</li>
</ul>

<h2>Data That May Be Retained</h2>

Some information may be retained when required by law or for fraud prevention,
security, or compliance purposes.

Any retained information will be securely stored and deleted once it is no longer required.

<h2>Deletion Time</h2>

Account deletion requests are typically completed within <strong>30 days</strong>.

